              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/747711-william?shelf=horror">horror</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/747711-william?shelf=serial-killer">serial-killer</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/747711-william?shelf=supernatural">supernatural</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/747711-william?shelf=e">e</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/747711-william?shelf=read-in-2011">read-in-2011</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer78660409" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9498607765310813843">I really enjoyed this book right up to the end and then found the ending very disappointing. I almost downgraded it to a three because of the ending. I found the premise to be pretty good but not original (serial killer executed at the same time a man dies and is revived from a heart attack.) There is lots of action and graphic description to please the not so faint of heart.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

