        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1902391004" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3425873821000702194">This is one seriously creepy book. Very graphic disturbing images of mutilation and murder. A haunting trip inside the mind of someone with multiple personalities. Which is a result of the killer being executed the same time another man is revived from a heart attack. It gets carried away sometimes when Saul goes into such intricate detail about the inner thoughts of the characters, but that actually made me laugh at times when the serial killer thought every little thing he did like turning on </span>
  <span id="freeText3425873821000702194" style="display:none">This is one seriously creepy book. Very graphic disturbing images of mutilation and murder. A haunting trip inside the mind of someone with multiple personalities. Which is a result of the killer being executed the same time another man is revived from a heart attack. It gets carried away sometimes when Saul goes into such intricate detail about the inner thoughts of the characters, but that actually made me laugh at times when the serial killer thought every little thing he did like turning on the news at a certain hour would tip his neighbors that he's the killer. All in all this is a very dark disturbing novel which I found excellent.</span>
  <a data-text-id="3425873821000702194" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

